    {
      "page_number": 3,
      "width": 612.0,
      "height": 792.0,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b2",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            89.33999633789062,
            90.11997985839844,
            531.7573852539062,
            576.1800537109375
          ],
          "text": "₹50/- per piece irrespective of the \ndenomination in addition to the loss. \n \nThe recovery of loss and imposition of \npenalty shall be done immediately on \ndetection, irrespective of number of \npieces. \niv. Non-compliance \nwith \noperational \nguidelines by currency chests detected \nby \nRBI \nofficials \ne.g. \n \na) Non-functioning of CCTV, non-\ncompliance with rules / guidelines \npertaining \nto \nCCTV, \nrecording \npreservation period and related issues \n \nb) Branch cash / documents kept in \nstrong \nroom \n(CC’s \nvault) \n \nc) Non-utilisation of Note Sorting \nMachines (NSMs) for sorting of notes \n(NSMs not used for sorting of high \ndenomination notes, i.e. notes of \ndenomination \n₹100 \nand \nabove, \nreceived over the counter or not used \nfor sorting notes remitted to chest / \nRBI) \n \nd) Non-conduct of surprise verification \nof currency chest balances - at (i) \nbimonthly \nintervals \nby \nofficials \nunconnected with the operations of \ncurrency chest, and (ii) six-monthly \nintervals \nby \nofficials \nfrom \nthe \nControlling Office",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b0",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            89.69999694824219,
            90.11997985839844,
            320.017333984375,
            106.4999771118164
          ],
          "text": "iii. Mutilated notes (including deliberately",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b1",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            111.66000366210938,
            103.92002868652344,
            320.01849365234375,
            147.89999389648438
          ],
          "text": "cut notes and built-up notes) detected \nin soiled note remittances and currency \nchest balances",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b3",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            321.17999267578125,
            187.1999969482422,
            531.7583618164062,
            313.97998046875
          ],
          "text": "Penalty of ₹5,000/- for each instance of \nirregularity. \n \nPenalty shall be enhanced to ₹10,000/- \nin case of repetition / recurrence of \nirregularity in consecutive inspection \ncycles or earlier. \n \nPenalty shall be levied immediately.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b4",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            245.36990356445312,
            335.3825378417969,
            365.90631103515625,
            455.9189147949219
          ],
          "text": "Withdrawn",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 28.0,
            "name": "Arial",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        }
      ],
      "links": []
    },
    {
